      "seed": 1877714969,
      "version": 439,
      "versionNonce": 952392537,
      "isDeleted": false,
      "boundElements": [],
      "updated": 1777754643935,
      "link": null,
      "locked": false,
      "text": "bot\n- topics\n    trigger based\n    rule based\n    onend, onstart, oninit\n- us, projops needed to manage bots\n- new platform topics were added that \n    changed expectations : e.g. oninit we were\n    supposed to call a initializer method in \n    intelligent control\n- freq regression, e.g preprod broke\n- in another repo : PVA, diff pipeline + release cycle\n",
      "fontSize": 16,
      "fontFamily": 5,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "containerId": null,
      "originalText": "bot\n- topics\n    trigger based\n    rule based\n    onend, onstart, oninit\n- us, projops needed to manage bots\n- new platform topics were added that \n    changed expectations : e.g. oninit we were\n    supposed to call a initializer method in \n    intelligent control\n- freq regression, e.g preprod broke\n- in another repo : PVA, diff pipeline + release cycle\n",
      "autoResize": true,
      "lineHeight": 1.25
    },
    {
      "id": "KkaRT8xdTI-FPLVzn40ZW",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 457.767050116919,
      "y": 418.3205343965625,
      "width": 304.687744140625,
      "height": 200,
      "angle": 0,
      "strokeColor": "#1e1e1e",
      "backgroundColor": "transparent",
      "fillStyle": "solid",
      "strokeWidth": 2,
      "strokeStyle": "solid",
      "roughness": 1,
      "opacity": 100,
      "groupIds": [],
      "frameId": null,
      "index": "aD",
      "roundness": null,
      "seed": 1152803063,
      "version": 405,
      "versionNonce": 1296710841,
      "isDeleted": false,
      "boundElements": [],
      "updated": 1777757495688,
      "link": null,
      "locked": false,
      "text": "Intelligent control\n- flaky, .e.g bot id null regression\n- diff repo + pipeline etc\n- layer between 1st party and mcs\n- shared code, often pattern mismatch\n- i had to establish pattern\n- often structure changes were \n    unannounced e.g router logic change\n- the layer to call capi->llm had to be \n    set by us : me.",
      "fontSize": 16,
      "fontFamily": 5,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "containerId": null,
      "originalText": "Intelligent control\n- flaky, .e.g bot id null regression\n- diff repo + pipeline etc\n- layer between 1st party and mcs\n- shared code, often pattern mismatch\n- i had to establish pattern\n- often structure changes were \n    unannounced e.g router logic change\n- the layer to call capi->llm had to be \n    set by us : me.",
      "autoResize": true,
      "lineHeight": 1.25
    },
    {
      "id": "Fcbd6r9pGss48ZF1zI3v-",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 79.45197011449511,
      "y": 379.8118287759461,
      "width": 353.2796936035156,
      "height": 240,
      "angle": 0,
      "strokeColor": "#1e1e1e",
      "backgroundColor": "transparent",
      "fillStyle": "solid",
      "strokeWidth": 2,
      "strokeStyle": "solid",
      "roughness": 1,
      "opacity": 100,
      "groupIds": [],
      "frameId": null,
      "index": "aE",
      "roundness": null,
      "seed": 1699916217,
      "version": 361,
      "versionNonce": 1243937463,
      "isDeleted": false,
      "boundElements": [],
      "updated": 1777755398560,
      "link": null,
      "locked": false,
      "text": "TE source : RE only\nsteps: RE + intersection wwith TE +\n    create\noptional : user can choose to gen comment\n    and edit\nadaptive card had many flaky, rendering issue\nI fugured out the multiline comment fix day\nbefore demo\nsidecar is implemented by IC, extended by \n    each owning team\n\n",
      "fontSize": 16,
      "fontFamily": 5,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "containerId": null,
      "originalText": "TE source : RE only\nsteps: RE + intersection wwith TE +\n    create\noptional : user can choose to gen comment\n    and edit\nadaptive card had many flaky, rendering issue\nI fugured out the multiline comment fix day\nbefore demo\nsidecar is implemented by IC, extended by \n    each owning team\n\n",
      "autoResize": true,
      "lineHeight": 1.25
    },
